></div>\n        <div class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[.25em] uppercase opacity-70 mb-2\" data-kid=\"115\">Author Q&amp;A · 30 sec</div>\n        <div class=\"font-display italic text-lg leading-snug\" data-kid=\"116\">\"I write the way a child folds paper —<br data-kid=\"117\">without knowing what shape it'll be.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"118\">\n          <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--ink)] overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"119\">\n            <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/ce7ef0d3f3c6435587c86ee5d70187f4.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"120\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&&__crawlAsset(this)\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"text-xs\" data-kid=\"121\">\n            <div class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"122\">Imogen Pell</div>\n            <div class=\"opacity-70\" data-kid=\"123\">author · 6 books</div>\n          </div>\n          <button class=\"ml-auto text-xs underline\" data-kid=\"124\">unfold ↗</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"col-span-2 relative flap-card p-5 rotate-[2deg] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center\" style=\"background:var(--pumpkin); color:var(--ink);\" data-kid=\"125\">\n        <div class=\"washi\" style=\"top:-10px; left:25%; transform:rotate(-6deg); background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(244,233,208,.7) 0 8px, rgba(244,233,208,.5) 8px 16px);\" data-kid=\"126\"></div>\n        <i class=\"ti ti-mail-opened text-4xl\" data-kid=\"127\"></i>\n        <div class=\"font-display font-bold text-base leading-tight mt-2\" data-kid=\"128\">Subscribe to The Folio</div>\n        <div class=\"text-[10px] mt-1 opacity-80\" data-kid=\"129\">a monthly paper letter</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"relative paper-mint torn-top torn-bottom py-28 px-8 mt-4\" data-kid=\"130\">\n  <div class=\"absolute inset-0 grain\" data-kid=\"131\"></div>\n  <div class=\"max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative\" data-kid=\"132\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-end justify-between mb-12\" data-kid=\"133\">\n      <div data-kid=\"134\">\n        <div class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[.3em] uppercase mb-3\" data-kid=\"135\">Featured Spread · No. 04</div>\n        <h2 class=\"font-display text-7xl font-black leading-[0.9]\" data-kid=\"136\">\n          The Rabbit who<br data-kid=\"137\">\n          <span class=\"italic-d font-light\" data-kid=\"138\">borrowed</span> the<br data-kid=\"139\">\n          <span class=\"text-[var(--crimson)]\" data-kid=\"140\">moon.</span>\n        </h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"max-w-sm text-right\" data-kid=\"141\">\n        <p class=\"font-display italic text-lg leading-snug\" data-kid=\"142\">A pinned, scroll-pulled chapter where a hare in a pocket-watch hat trades hours for stars.</p>\n        <div class=\"mt-4 flex justify-end gap-2\" data-kid=\"143\">\n          <span class=\"chip\" data-kid=\"144\">illustrated</span>\n          <span class=\"chip\" style=\"background:var(--cream)\" data-kid=\"145\">32 pp</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"relative h-[560px] grid grid-cols-2 border-2 border-[var(--ink)] paper overflow-hidden fold-shadow rounded-[40px_60px_40px_60px]\" data-kid=\"146\">\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 grain\" data-kid=\"147\"></div>\n      <div class=\"spine\" data-kid=\"148\"></div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"relative p-12\" data-kid=\"149\">\n        <div class=\"absolute top-6 left-6 text-[10px] tracking-[.3em] uppercase\" data-kid=\"150\">Chapter I</div>\n        <div class=\"mt-12\" data-kid=\"151\">\n          <p class=\"font-display italic text-2xl leading-snug max-w-sm\" data-kid=\"152\">\n            \"Tonight,\" said the rabbit, lifting his hat, \"the moon will be in here. Just for safe keeping.\"\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"153\">\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[var(--crimson)] border-2 border-[var(--ink)] flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"154\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right text-[var(--cream)]\" data-kid=\"155\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" data-kid=\"156\">Continue the spread</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-36 h-36 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-[var(--ink)] pop-shadow rotate-[-12deg]\" data-kid=\"157\">\n          <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/5afded92fe554971a882e5d3d3c4ce01.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"158\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&&__crawlAsset(this)\">\n        </div>\n        \n        <svg class=\"absolute top-1/2 right-8 w-14 h-14 text-[var(--pumpkin)]\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" data-kid=\"159\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5L18.2 22 12 17.5 5.8 22l2.4-8.1L2 9.4h7.6z\" data-kid=\"160\"></path></svg>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"relative p-12\" data-kid=\"161\">\n        <div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 text-[10px] tracking-[.3em] uppercase\" data-kid=\"162\">Plate IV</div>\n        <div class=\"absolute right-10 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2\" data-kid=\"163\">\n          <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"164\">\n            <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/898fe710d1fb4b379e807c5be9c7abe3.png\" class=\"w-[300px] h-[400px] object-cover border-[3px] border-[var(--ink)] pop-shadow\" style=\"clip-path: polygon(6% 2%, 32% 0, 60% 3%, 88% 1%, 100% 12%, 98% 38%, 100% 65%, 97% 92%, 78% 100%, 50% 97%, 22% 100%, 4% 96%, 0 75%, 2% 50%, 0 25%, 3% 6%);\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"165\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&