\"183\">Conversations<br data-kid=\"184\"><span class=\"italic-d\" data-kid=\"185\">in the margins.</span></h2>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"text-sm underline font-medium\" href=\"#\" data-kid=\"186\">see the entire studio →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"relative h-[700px]\" data-kid=\"187\">\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute left-[2%] top-[5%] rotate-[-3deg] w-[280px]\" data-kid=\"188\">\n        <div class=\"relative w-44 h-52 mx-auto border-[3px] border-[var(--ink)] overflow-hidden pop-shadow\" style=\"clip-path: polygon(8% 2%, 50% 0, 92% 4%, 100% 30%, 97% 70%, 100% 96%, 60% 100%, 20% 98%, 0 80%, 3% 40%, 0 10%); background: var(--mint);\" data-kid=\"189\">\n          <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/1c7d073d735b4a9cbe823f99bba1acf0.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"190\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&&__crawlAsset(this)\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bubble mt-6\" data-kid=\"191\">\n          <p class=\"font-display italic text-base leading-snug\" data-kid=\"192\">\"I draw with my left hand so my right hand can keep secrets.\"</p>\n          <div class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase\" data-kid=\"193\">Léon Brassart</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute left-[28%] top-[2%] rotate-[2deg] w-[300px]\" data-kid=\"194\">\n        <div class=\"relative w-48 h-56 mx-auto border-[3px] border-[var(--ink)] overflow-hidden pop-shadow\" style=\"clip-path: polygon(5% 4%, 55% 0, 95% 3%, 100% 38%, 96% 75%, 100% 98%, 50% 100%, 8% 96%, 0 60%, 4% 22%); background: var(--cream-2);\" data-kid=\"195\">\n          <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/b18829f8d08f4579ac5ca673b6aef34f.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"196\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&&__crawlAsset(this)\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bubble right mt-6 ml-12\" data-kid=\"197\">\n          <p class=\"font-display italic text-base leading-snug\" data-kid=\"198\">\"Children read pictures the way archaeologists read bones.\"</p>\n          <div class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase\" data-kid=\"199\">Imogen Pell</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute right-[20%] top-[8%] rotate-[-2deg] w-[300px]\" data-kid=\"200\">\n        <div class=\"relative w-44 h-52 mx-auto border-[3px] border-[var(--ink)] overflow-hidden pop-shadow\" style=\"clip-path: polygon(10% 0, 55% 4%, 95% 0, 100% 35%, 98% 72%, 100% 100%, 55% 96%, 5% 100%, 0 65%, 4% 18%); background: var(--pumpkin);\" data-kid=\"201\">\n            <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/b61d2fc4331a460493d2f2d56cbeed36.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"202\" onerror=\"__crawlAsset&&__crawlAsset(this)\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bubble mt-6\" data-kid=\"203\">\n          <p class=\"font-display italic text-base leading-snug\" data-kid=\"204\">\"I keep a pocket of unwritten words. They jingle.\"</p>\n          <div class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase\" data-kid=\"205\">Otto Hjelm</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute left-[8%] bottom-[2%] rotate-[3deg] w-[280px]\" data-kid=\"206\">\n        <div class=\"relative w-44 h-52 mx-auto border-[3px] border-[var(--ink)] overflow-hidden pop-shadow\" style=\"clip-path: polygon(6% 6%, 48% 0, 94% 5%, 100% 40%, 95% 80%, 100% 100%, 56% 96%, 12% 100%, 0 70%, 5% 28%); background: var(--crimson);\" data-kid=\"207\">\n            <img src=\"https://kombai-assets-dev.b-cdn.net/generated_assets/a993fd29-0101-46bc-9b8b-13bc576c1070/28ddfae3b67e40c9b760098467ea7f69.png\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt decoding=\"async\" loading=